author: Kam Dhillon
title: Louis Vuitton Showcases SS17 Hits in High-Octane ‘SENSE’ Editorial
text:
Visit the original post to see all 6 images from this gallery. 
Location: Tokyo, Japan
Season: Spring/Summer 2017
Key Looks: the vibrant mohair knit in slide #2, the safari-ready, monogrammed backpack in slide #6, and those luxe creepers in slide #1.
Editor’s Notes: Louis Vuitton has teamed up with Japanese fashion publication SENSE for an editorial featuring its SS17 collection. The French house’s tailored hits are given the high-octane treatment, honing focus on luxurious exotic skins, electric-blue zebra prints, and its punk-inspired references.
